( priest)
THE LORD BE WITH YOU.

52:10.160 --> 52:13.254
MOM, FEDERICO'S GONNA
DRIVE YOU BACK, OKAY ?

52:13.260 --> 52:15.558
I JUST NEED TO GO OVER
A FEW DETAILS WITH NATE.

52:15.560 --> 52:17.323
WE'LL BE
RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

52:17.330 --> 52:19.321
PUT HER THERE,
MRS. F.

52:19.330 --> 52:23.255
YOU HAVE SUCH
DELICATE HANDS, FEDERICO.

52:23.260 --> 52:25.490
LIKE A STATUE.

52:25.500 --> 52:29.152
OR AN ILLUSTRATION
IN AN ANTIQUE BOOK.

52:29.160 --> 52:31.526
OR ONE OF THOSE
LI((LE CERAMIC HANDS

52:31.530 --> 52:33.896
THEY USE TO
DISPLAY GLOVES.

52:43.860 --> 52:46.397
YOU WANT TO BE
THE ALPHA DOG, NATE,
IS THAT IT ?

52:46.400 --> 52:49.790
COASTING TOWARD MID-LIFE
WITH NOTHING TO SHOW FOR IT

52:49.800 --> 52:51.529
AND NOW YOU WANT
TO COME BACK

52:51.530 --> 52:53.896
AND BE THE ROCK FOR
THIS FAMILY TO LEAN ON ?

52:53.900 --> 52:54.696
FUCK YOU.

52:54.700 --> 52:55.553
THAT IS NOT
WHAT I'M--

52:55.560 --> 52:57.448
YOU WANT TO
GET YOUR HANDS DIRTY ?

52:57.460 --> 52:59.223
YOU SANCTIMONIOUS
PRICK, TALK TO ME

52:59.230 --> 53:01.494
WHEN YOU'VE HAD TO STUFF
FORMALDEHYDE SOAKED COTTON

53:01.500 --> 53:04.025
UP YOUR FATHER'S ASS
SO HE DOESN'T LEAK.

53:04.030 --> 53:05.452
JESUS.

53:05.460 --> 53:06.859
YEAH, WELL,

53:06.860 --> 53:08.623
I'M SURE YOU JUST
WOULD'VE TOSSED HIM OUT
WITH THE GARBAGE.

53:08.630 --> 53:11.224
IT MAY SEEM
WEIRD TO YOU,

53:11.230 --> 53:15.018
BUT THERE IS A REASON BEHIND
EVERYTHING THAT WE DO HERE.

53:15.030 --> 53:16.054
WE PROVIDE PEOPLE

53:16.060 --> 53:18.893
WITH A VERY IMPORTANT
AND SACRED SERVICE

53:18.900 --> 53:20.993
AT THE DARKEST TIME
IN THEIR LIVES.

53:21.000 --> 53:23.798
BECAUSE MAYBE THEY DON'T WANT TO
MAKE A SPECTACLE OF THEMSELVES.

53:23.800 --> 53:26.689
BECAUSE MAYBE THEY'D PREFER
TO GRIEVE IN PRIVATE.

53:26.700 --> 53:28.156
WHY ?!

53:28.160 --> 53:29.957
WHY DOES IT HAVE TO BE
SUCH A SECRET ?

53:29.960 --> 53:32.155
IT'S NOTHING
TO BE ASHAMED OF.

53:32.160 --> 53:34.196
DAVE, PLEASE--

53:34.200 --> 53:35.895
YOU KNOW NOTHING !

53:35.900 --> 53:38.027
NOTHING !

53:40.430 --> 53:43.820
YOU HAD A RESPONSIBILITY
TO THIS FAMILY

53:43.830 --> 53:47.994
AND YOU RAN AWAY FROM IT
AND YOU LEFT IT ALL FOR ME.

53:48.000 --> 53:50.924
WHOA, DON'T BLAME ME IF YOU'RE
NOT LIVING THE LIFE YOU WANT.

53:50.930 --> 53:53.398
THAT IS NOBODY'S FAULT
BUT YOUR OWN.

53:56.360 --> 54:00.421
OKAY, FINE, JUST
DO ME A FAVOR, OKAY ?

54:00.430 --> 54:02.853
YOU GOT OUT...

54:02.860 --> 54:05.021
STAY OUT.

54:10.400 --> 54:12.493
EXCUSE ME,
MR. FISHER, SIR ?

54:12.500 --> 54:14.092
IF I COULD JUST GET
A MOMENT OF YOUR TIME.

54:14.100 --> 54:15.294
WHAT ?

54:15.300 --> 54:16.756
I'M FROM CROEHNER
SERVICE INTERNATIONAL.

54:16.760 --> 54:18.796
I'D LIKE TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT THE ADVANTAGES

54:18.800 --> 54:20.893
OF JOINING OUR FAMILY
OF DEATH CARE FACILITIES.

54:20.900 --> 54:22.356
I DON'T
BELIEVE THIS.

54:22.360 --> 54:23.520
SIR, IF YOU'D
JUST HEAR ME OUT--

54:23.530 --> 54:25.293
WE'RE NOT SELLING,
NOW GET THE FUCK OUT OF HERE.

54:25.300 --> 54:27.097
WE WOULDN'T CHANGE THE NAME
OF THE BUSINESS.

54:27.100 --> 54:29.125
AND OF COURSE,
WE WOULD RETAIN YOU
AS A SALARIED MANAGER.

54:29.130 --> 54:31.325
LOOK, I REALLY WANT TO
HIT SOMEBODY RIGHT NOW

54:31.330 --> 54:33.127
AND IT MIGHT
AS WELL BE YOU !

54:38.230 --> 54:40.425
I'LL CALL YA

54:40.430 --> 54:43.422
WHEN YOU'VE HAD SOME TIME
TO RECOVER FROM YOUR LOSS.

54:47.700 --> 54:49.691
YOU'RE REALLY LUCKY,
YOU KNOW THAT ?

54:49.700 --> 54:50.792
ARE YOU KIDDING ?

54:50.800 --> 54:52.552
IT WAS OVER
IN A SECOND.

54:52.560 --> 54:53.788
I DIDN'T HAVE TO
BE AFRAID OF IT,

54:53.800 --> 54:55.290
I DIDN'T EVEN HAVE TO
THINK ABOUT IT.

54:55.300 --> 54:57.052
NO MORE BULLSHIT.

54:57.060 --> 54:58.550
NO MORE
RESPONSIBILITY.

54:58.560 --> 55:00.323
AND NO MORE
HAVING TO CARE.

55:00.330 --> 55:02.321
NO MORE BOREDOM !

55:02.330 --> 55:05.026
NO MORE
WAITING TO DIE.

55:32.560 --> 55:33.925
HI.

55:36.760 --> 55:38.819
WELL, AFTER FOUR DAYS
WITH MY FAMILY

55:38.830 --> 55:40.957
I'M READY FOR
SHOCK THERAPY.

55:40.960 --> 55:44.350
I'M JUST WAITING TO SEE IF
MY HMO COVERS IT.

55:46.430 --> 55:48.159
HOW'S IT GOING
WITH YOU ?

55:48.160 --> 55:51.425
OH, IT'S GREAT, GREAT.

55:51.430 --> 55:54.297
MY FATHER'S DEAD,
MY MOM'S A WHORE,

55:54.300 --> 55:55.551
MY BROTHER WANTS
TO KILL ME,

55:55.560 --> 55:57.551
AND MY SISTER'S
SMOKING CRACK,

55:57.560 --> 55:59.528
I THINK I WIN.

55:59.530 --> 56:02.192
FOUR DAYS AGO I WAS
A RELATIVELY HAPPY GUY,

56:02.200 --> 56:05.294
AND NOW, IT'S LIKE I DON'T
EVEN KNOW WHO THAT GUY WAS.

56:12.030 --> 56:13.850
I'M A FUCKING MESS.

56:13.860 --> 56:16.249
IF YOU WANT TO
KNOW THE TRUTH.

56:16.260 --> 56:18.797
BUT, I THINK YOU'RE
ALREADY AWARE OF THAT.

56:24.230 --> 56:26.596
WELL, HERE'S
MY NUMBER.

56:26.600 --> 56:28.795
IF YOU EVER WANT TO,
I DON'T KNOW,

56:28.800 --> 56:31.496
GO OUT ON
A REAL DATE ?

56:31.500 --> 56:33.752
YOU KNOW, WHERE
YOU BUY ME DINNER

56:33.760 --> 56:35.751
BEFORE I PUT OUT.

56:39.800 --> 56:41.358
MAYBE I'M ONE
OF THOSE WOMEN

56:41.360 --> 56:43.590
THAT MEETS A MAN WHO SEEMS
EMOTIONALLY CON FLICT ED,

56:43.600 --> 56:45.329
NO RELATIONSHIP SKILLS
AND I FIGURE,

56:45.330 --> 56:47.525
"HEY, THAT'S FOR ME."

56:47.530 --> 56:49.623
I DON'T EVEN LIVE HERE,
I LIVE IN SEATTLE.

56:49.630 --> 56:51.154
SEE, THAT JUST MAKES
YOU MORE ATTRACTIVE.

56:51.160 --> 56:51.990
REALLY ?

56:52.000 --> 56:53.524
OH, YEAH.

56:53.530 --> 56:56.590
WELL, I ALSO HAPPEN
TO BE A SERIAL RAPIST.

56:56.600 --> 56:59.694
I'VE GOT 10 NURSES
BURIED UNDER MY HOUSE.

56:59.700 --> 57:02.419
NOW YOU'RE
MAKING ME WET.

57:36.560 --> 57:38.858
WHOA, WHOA.

57:41.930 --> 57:45.093
I, I NEED...

57:45.100 --> 57:47.250
I NEED...

58:03.230 --> 58:03.252
IT'S OKAY,
IT'S OKAY.

58:59.830 --> 59:01.752
GOOD MORNING.

59:07.830 --> 59:10.424
THANK GOD
YOU'RE HERE.

59:10.430 --> 59:14.218
YEAH, WELL,
OF COURSE I'M HERE.

59:21.330 --> 59:23.594
WHAT DO YOU WANT
FOR BREAKFAST ?

59:23.600 --> 59:25.090
OH, I'M GONNA
GO FOR A RUN.

59:25.100 --> 59:26.499
I'LL EAT WHEN
I GET BACK.

59:26.500 --> 59:27.398
NATE ?

59:27.400 --> 59:28.822
YEP ?

59:28.830 --> 59:31.321
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
GO BACK TO SEATTLE

59:31.330 --> 59:33.195
RIGHT AWAY, DO YOU ?

59:33.200 --> 59:35.122
UH...

59:38.160 --> 59:39.798
I GUESS NOT.

59:39.800 --> 59:41.256
I COULD MAKE
A FEW CALLS.

59:41.260 --> 59:43.524
THANK YOU.

59:43.530 --> 59:45.623
YEAH, SURE.

59:45.630 --> 59:48.326
JUST FOR
A FEW DAYS.

59:52.400 --> 59:54.220
OKAY.

1:00:35.930 --> 1:00:38.251
WAITING
AT THE STATION

1:00:41.930 --> 1:00:45.195
WAITING
FOR THE RIGHT MOVES

1:00:50.000 --> 1:00:52.150
WAITING

1:00:53.330 --> 1:00:56.458
AND IF YOU EVER
CHANGE YOUR MIND

1:00:58.700 --> 1:01:01.919
YOU KNOW I'M NOT
HARD TO FIND

1:01:04.130 --> 1:01:08.021
AND IF YOU EVER
NEED SOMEONE

1:01:08.030 --> 1:01:10.851
I'LL STILL
BE WAITING

1:01:14.400 --> 1:01:17.119
WAITING
WITH THE ORPHANS

1:01:20.630 --> 1:01:23.849
WAITING
FOR THE BEE STINGS

1:01:26.730 --> 1:01:30.791
THEY TELL ME
THAT SUCCESS BRINGS

1:01:32.830 --> 1:01:36.254
WAITING
IN THE HIGH FLIGHT

1:01:39.200 --> 1:01:41.828
WAITING THROUGH
YOUR WHOLE LIFE

1:01:53.000 --> 1:01:55.457
JUST WAITING

1:02:44.760 --> 1:02:45.749
lmjm
